    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "lgb",
      "x": 1656.2647100370075,
      "y": 362.434244277637,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 332,
      "text": "意图　≈ GUI　·　chat / 命令\n\nAgent 内核　= CPU　·　Claude\n\n程序　≈ 源代码　·　SKILL.md\n（改一句话就改了软件）\n\n能力　≈ SDK 调用　·　extract·score·ws_*\n\n上下文+记忆　= RAM　·　Active context·reviewed\n\n文件系统总线　= 磁盘 + 接口　·　存储即接口：核心对象本来就是文件，MCP 暴露成 ls/read/grep，一次打通全部 CRUD（无需 list_models 等几十个专用 API）\n\n纠正闭环　·　score·save_reviewed·autoresearch\n\n能力包　·　/plugin install · Upload plugin",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "version": 295,
      "versionNonce": 1808162226,
      "index": "b09",
      "isDeleted": false,
